ấn - 哭韋大夫之晉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/T%E1%BA%A3-thi%C3%AAn-ch%C3%AD-Lam-Quan-th%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87t-t%C3%B4n-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-9lHaFLSlQpvUWWOiZ5-bag">Tả thiên chí Lam Quan thị điệt tôn Tương - 左遷至藍關示姪孫湘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quang-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/T%E1%BA%B7ng-b%E1%BA%AFc-s%E1%BB%A9-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-L%C3%BD-Ch%E1%BA%A5n-V%C4%83n-%C4%91%E1%BA%B3ng/poem-cBncbAoimuAY1T-UE9-Mww">Tặng bắc sứ Sài Trang Khanh, Lý Chấn Văn đẳng - 贈北使柴莊卿，李振文等</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quang-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-X3Oume1_mYQvTGcgMAhydQ">Trần Quang Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/X%C3%ADch-ti%C3%AAu-h%C3%A0nh/poem-33uuOJp8vr-OjWdKIKiuKw">Xích tiêu hành - 赤霄行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
